FBIS3-5180 "dreas043_n_94001" FBIS-EAS-94-043 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Mar 1994 Vietnam Hanoi on U.S. `Initial Steps' To Restore Ties BK0403103794 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam in English 1000 GMT 4 Mar 94 BK0403103794 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] The American WALL STREET Journal on Thursday reported that Vietnam and the United States agreed at Hanoi talks in principle to open liaison offices and to discuss the return of properties left over from the war. Meanwhile, the United States Government on Friday said the two countries had taken initial steps to restore full diplomatic relations when the two sides agreed in principle to open liaison offices.
